Hi, I was going through a few issues in CorpusLoaders.jl, one of them was regarding the addition of NER Datasets namely GMB, WiNER, EWNERTC, WNUT17, etc. 
I feel that the EWNERTC dataset could be a very good addition. Should I start working on it?
